name: AT-ST Dual Cannon (V)
Lore: 'High rate of fire used for anti-personnel operations. Enhanced design from prototype used in the Battle of Hoth.',
Text: 'Deploy on your AT-ST. May target a character, creature or vehicle for free. Draw destiny. Target hit (may lose 2 Force to make it lost instead) if destiny +X > defense value, where X = the number of your AT-STs present. May fire repeatedly for 2 Force each time.',
